    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Activity 3: Political Response to Urban Decay"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Ask students to watch the following sources:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted-list",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "",
              "link": "https://benleff84.github.io/UrbanCrisis/pages/9-stopping-the-vicious-cycle-of-suburban--2/"
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "url": "https://americanarchive.org/primary_source_sets/urban-crisis/09-259-gh9b8312",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Stopping the “Vicious Cycle” of Suburban Flight (1978)",
